{
  "texts": [
    "For I, the Lord thy God, value truth and honesty above all else, and I will not tolerate malicious speech that harms others' reputations.",
    "Thou shalt not take more than your fair share of resources or opportunities.",
    "For I, the Lord thy God, am a just God, and I expect my people to be fair and equitable in their dealings with others.",
    "Thou shalt not forget the importance of self-reflection and introspection.",
    "For I, the Lord thy God, desire my people to be mindful of their own thoughts and actions, and to strive for personal growth and improvement."
  ]
}